text: Elie Naasan (2 June 1931 - 4 April 2015) was a Lebanese wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Lebanese male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Lebanon Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from İskenderun
